---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import LeadForm from '@/components/LeadForm.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Selling your Asheville-area home"
  description="Pricing strategy, prep coordination, and a marketing plan that gets the right buyers through the door. With Karin Wulff at Nexus Realty."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 sm:py-20">
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-sun-600">Selling</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl text-mountain-900 sm:text-5xl">
      A pricing strategy, a prep crew, and a marketing plan.
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-prose text-lg text-mountain-600">
      Selling your home in WNC isn't just listing it. It's the prep, the photos,
      the staging, the pricing decision, and the marketing reach. I run all of it —
      so you're not coordinating five vendors yourself.
    </p>

    <section class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-mountain-900">Pricing strategy</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-mountain-700">
        I'll prepare a detailed comparative market analysis (CMA) using the actual
        comps in your micro-market — not a Zillow estimate. We'll talk through three
        strategies (aggressive-for-speed, market-price, aspirational) and pick the one
        that matches your timeline and goals.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-10">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-mountain-900">Prep, staging, and photography</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-mountain-700">
        I have a small group of photographers, stagers, painters, and contractors I trust.
        We'll walk through the house together, agree on what's worth doing, and I'll
        coordinate the schedule so it's done before listing photos.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-10">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-mountain-900">Marketing &amp; reach</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-mountain-700">
        Beyond the MLS — featured placement on AVL Curious, targeted ads to relocator
        audiences, and the usual portal syndication. Premium homes get premium attention.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-10">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-mountain-900">My recent sold record</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-mountain-700">
        Recent transactions and reviews are visible on my
        <a href="https://www.zillow.com/profile/wolfgrl1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zillow profile</a>
        and <a href="https://www.homes.com/real-estate-agents/karin-wulff/el9tr5p/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Homes.com profile</a>.
        A curated <code>/sold/</code> page is coming as we publish more transactions here directly.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="mt-16">
      <LeadForm source="sell-bottom" heading="Curious what your home would list for?" blurb="Drop your address and timeline and I'll come back with a free, real-comp market analysis." />
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
